<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tom Comic</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: white;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .rainbow-text {
            font-size: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, violet);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .box {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

            .box img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 200px;
                object-fit: cover;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

            .box p {
                margin-top: 10px;
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 1.5;
                color: #555;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="rainbow-text">Tom Comic</h1>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="box">
                <img src="LINK_HINH_1" alt="Ảnh 1">
                <p>Diam dolor diam ipsum et, tempor volutpat sit consectetur sit. Aliquyam diam amet diam et eos sadipscing labore.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <img src="LINK_HINH_2" alt="Ảnh 2">
                <p>Sanctus clita duo justo et tempor consetetur takimata elitr. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <img src="LINK_HINH_3" alt="Ảnh 3">
                <p>Cita erat ipsum et lorem et sit, sed stet no labore lorem sit. Clita erat ipsum et lorem.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
